         directly in bin\ (flattened via Link) and must match PlatformTarget
         above. If your IIS app pool runs in 32-bit mode, point both the
         PlatformTarget above and these two paths at Lib\native\x86\ instead. -->
    <None Include="Lib\native\x64\MFS100Dll.dll">
